      "role": "user",
      "content": "it’s weird how quiet it gets here. i spend 10 hours a day staring at screens and chatting with people i’ll never meet, and then i just... turn the monitor off. and it's like i didn't even exist during the day. i feel like if i just stopped showing up, everyone would just keep typing and the world wouldn't even skip a beat. like i'm just a glitch in the system that finally got patched out.",
